headline: Is eBay Stock Still an Opportunity After 42% Jump in 2025?
summary: Thinking about what to do with your eBay stock? You are not alone. After all, it has been quite a ride for investors lately, and it is only natural to want some clarity before your next move. eBay has seen its share price jump a remarkable 42.2% year-to-date, with a solid 35.6% gain over the last 12 months. Even stretching back three and five years, the numbers make for impressive reading, up 153.3% and 73.0%, respectively. That said, the last month and week have been a little bumpy, dipping...
